name: DottedStrokeStyles
shortdesc: A collection of dotted stroke styles.

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.shortdesc: Initial values for properties of the new DottedStrokeStyle (Optional)

method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the DottedStrokeStyle.

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the DottedStrokeStyle with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.shortdesc: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

method.name: itemByName
method.shortdesc: Returns the DottedStrokeStyle with the specified name.

method.name: itemByID
method.shortdesc: Returns the DottedStrokeStyle with the specified ID.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the DottedStrokeStyles within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.shortdesc: The DottedStrokeStyle, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: DottedStrokeStyle, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.shortdesc: The DottedStrokeStyle, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: DottedStrokeStyle, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first DottedStrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: lastItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the last DottedStrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: middleItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the middle DottedStrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the DottedStrokeStyle with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The index of the DottedStrokeStyle that follows the desired DottedStrokeStyle.

method.name: nextItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the DottedStrokeStyle whose index follows the specified DottedStrokeStyle in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The DottedStrokeStyle whose index comes before the desired DottedStrokeStyle.

method.name: anyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns any DottedStrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every DottedStrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: toSource
method.shortdesc: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the DottedStrokeStyle.
Returns the DottedStrokeStyle with the specified index.

property.name: length
property.shortdesc: The number of objects in the collection.
